data.description: Last of the highly sought after Braselton quality builds in Rancho Vista! Beautifully maintained Rancho Vista home!  This four bedroom (could be 5), three bath home sits on a large, corner lot with room for a pool!  Open floor plan with separated bedrooms for privacy, fireplace and laminate tile flooring. The island cook's kitchen has a breakfast bar, granite countertops, upgraded, stainless steel appliances with 4-burner gas stove, tumbled marble backsplash, large walk-in pantry and lots of cabinet storage.  Master bedroom has double, his and hers walk-in closets and French doors that open to a large, master bath with dual sinks, a large, tiled shower complete with triple shower heads and an abundance of natural light!  Upstairs is a large room, which could be a bedroom, office, game room and is complete with its' own full bath.  Oversized laundry room and mud room/drop off zone.  Three sides brick with back hardy board with oversized garage.
